Documents All Pairs Similarity
map (doc_id, document):
for each term t in document:
emit (t, [doc_id,document] )
reduce (t, docs: list[ [doc_id,document] ] ):
for id1,d1 in docs:
for id2,d2 in docs:
if s(d1,d2)>=tau:
emit ( [id1, id2], s(d1,d2) )
Note that the full document is sent from mappers to reducers to compute similarities.
