map (doc_id, document):
for each term t in sorted(document):
if t>b(document):
emit (t, [doc_id,document] )
reduce (t, docs: list[ [doc_id,document] ] ):
for id1,d1 in docs:
for id2,d2 in docs:
if ( t == max( intersect(d1,d2) ) ):
if s(d1,d2)>=tau:
emit ( [id1, id2], s(d1,d2) )
Note: the test on the intersection will be true only for one reducer.
